OL,3,CLockerbie set to receive temporary
OL,4,C20mph speed limit
OL,6,FLockerbie is set to be the the next
OL,7,Ftown in Dumfries and Galloway to
OL,8,Freceive a temporary 20mph speed limit.
OL,10,FIts part of a national strategy across
OL,11,FScotland to ensure all appropriate
OL,12,Froads in built-up areas will have a
OL,13,Fsafer speed limit of 20mph by the end
OL,14,Fof 2025.
OL,16,FThe temporarily enforced speed limits
OL,17,Fwill help consult on which roads will
OL,18,Fbe included.
