OL,3,CLockerbie set to receive temporary
OL,4,C20mph speed limit
OL,6,FStarting on 26 July, ahead of the
OL,7,Fschools returning in August Lockerbie
OL,8,Fwill be under the temporary 20mph
OL,9,Flimit.
OL,11,FThe introduction of the new speed
OL,12,Flimit aims to reduce perceptions of
OL,13,Froad danger, while encouraging people
OL,14,Fto walk, wheel and cycle. It will also
OL,15,Fseek to encourage considerate and
OL,16,Frespectful driving within Lockerbie
OL,17,Fand create a safer experience for
OL,18,Flocals and visitors.
