OL,3,CLockerbie set to receive temporary
OL,4,C20mph speed limit
OL,6,FCouncillor Gail Macgregor, Leader of
OL,7,FDumfries and Galloway Council said:
OL,8,F"Following on from the successful
OL,9,Fimplementation of both Stranraer and
OL,10,FAnnan's 20mph speed limit schemes, a
OL,11,F20mph limit for Lockerbie will not
OL,12,Fonly reduce vehicle speeds and
OL,13,Faccidents, but also make the roads and
OL,14,Fstreets more attractive and safer for
OL,15,Factive travel and vulnerable user
OL,16,Fgroups.
OL,18,F"The Annan 20mph scheme has resulted
OL,19,Fin initial speed reductions of up to
OL,20,F20% at some survey sites.
