OL,6,F"We aim to replicate this success in
OL,7,FLockerbie and encourage more people to
OL,8,Freduce their speed and drive more
OL,9,Fconsiderately.
OL,11,F"Lowering traffic speed supports our
OL,12,Flocal towns and villages to be places
OL,13,Fwhere people are free to travel in
OL,14,Fways that are safe, sustainable,
OL,15,Fhealthy and fair."
